    "The application of segmented flow or microslug reactors was demonstrated in the decarboxylative arylation cross-coupling reaction promoted by catalysts and light [40].",
    "The design allows the screening to be more material-and time-efficient in the optimization of both continuous variables (e.g., temperature and residence time) and discrete variables (e.g., catalyst, base).",
